YouTube star David Dobrik has surprised his best friend, Heath Hussar by giving him a brand new Lamborghini Huracán as birthday gift. Dobrik who is one of the biggest YouTube vloggers with over 13 million subscribers, partnered with EA to promote the launch of the new Need For Speed game ‘Heat’. On Tuesday, David Dobrik uploaded a touching video, revealing Heath Hussar gift to other friends first, who were all pretty envious, before finally unveiling the Lamborghini Huracán, complete with a big red bow, to him on his birthday. On seeing his luxury birthday gift, Heath couldn’t believe it was real, but after he was assured this wasn’t a prank, he broke down in tears.